data.description: Discover this sun-drenched 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo in the heart of booming Woodlawn. Recently updated with refinished floors and fresh paint, new dishwasher and microwave, this unit offers ample storage space, and a bonus storage closet in the basement. The spacious primary suite boasts a double vanity and a luxurious 6-foot soaker tub with jets. And an in-unit washer-dryer. Enjoy the convenience of being just a short distance away from the University of Chicago, the upcoming Obama Library, CTA, Metra, and University of Chicago shuttle buses. Woodlawn offers a plethora of nearby amenities, including parks, playlots, and is just a quick 5-minute drive to the lakefront, bike trails, The Museum of Science and Industry, Lakeshore Drive, golf courses, grocery stores, restaurants, and more. Parking is a breeze with a deeded, secure parking space included in the price plus easy street parking. Don't miss out on this fantastic property in a vibrant, growing community!
